rmion modes localized at the fixed point needed to cancel\nthe quadratic divergences from the Yukawa interactions. The cutoff scale of the\ntheory could be a few times 10 TeV.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 9 Oct 2002 18:09:17 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 4 Jun 2003 17:50:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2008-11-26"}
